Parliament, Thursday, 18 June 2020 – The Portfolio Committee on Higher Education, Science and Technology will tomorrow receive an update briefing from the Minister of Higher Education, Science and Technology, Dr Blade Nzimande, on the committee’s request that the salaries of the vice chancellors be reviewed.
	
	The committee will be briefed on various issues including the Ministerial Task Team on the review of the National Student Financial Aid Scheme, the historic debt, and standardisation of the Student Representative Councils’ elections.
	
	Details of the meeting:
	Date: Friday, 19 June 2020
	Time: 09h00 – 12h00 noon
	
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON, MR PHILLY MAPULANE.
	
